Package edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.util

Class Log<E>

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.util.Log<E>
Type Parameters:
E - a generic type to work with any type
All Implemented Interfaces:
ILog<E>
public class Log<E> extends Object implements ILog<E>
An Array based list that maintains a log of information. Implements ILog, thus elements added to the log also cannot be removed. Utilizes an array-based approach.
Author:
Jeremiah Knizley, Ryan McPhee
